{"id": 2334, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都遇到过哪些职场友谊难题?", "description": "办公室可能是你呆的时间最久的地方，和那儿的人相处的过程中都遇到过哪些困扰？(题图来自：视觉中国）", "record_count": 2467, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180507175419MdH8YoO3xrq1eCRy.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-06-04T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 285955, "content": "每天都要伪装一副面具", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094614}, {"id": 289035, "content": "同事就是同事 为什么非得当朋友 每天尴尬而不失礼貌的聊天就足够了 为什么非得当朋友？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1344761}, {"id": 287244, "content": "最讨厌小人得志 搞是非", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1374336}, {"id": 289044, "content": "职场有友谊吗？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1383050}, {"id": 285727, "content": "直属领导说要按朋友方式相处……涨薪和升职时候除外。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366453}, {"id": 288800, "content": "讨厌一个人极致却还要每天和她尬笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380759}, {"id": 321070, "content": "自以为跟我关系好的同事问我工资", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 820731}, {"id": 286514, "content": "哈哈", "image": "img/option/option/20180611155749zw8pbYfAOGje4x2v.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371303}, {"id": 285245, "content": "不知道孰真孰假，一开始挺相信，到后来才发觉被骗！", "image": null, "praise_count": 90, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970221}, {"id": 285247, "content": "朋友和同事要分开 前同事可以做朋友 但千万不要拉朋友做同事或共创业", "image": null, "praise_count": 244, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 966594}, {"id": 285248, "content": "明明没那么熟，老搞什么聚会，下班各回各家不好吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 682, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}, {"id": 285249, "content": "同事很难同道，成为朋友还是需要三观、志趣差不多才行。", "image": null, "praise_count": 69, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1347848}, {"id": 285250, "content": "直属领导能做朋友吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252535}, {"id": 285253, "content": "bitch把我和我朋友分开了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 748704}, {"id": 285260, "content": "有时想说点掏心窝的话，倾诉完就后悔", "image": null, "praise_count": 208, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 894776}, {"id": 285261, "content": "职场就不要谈友谊了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 167, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 630956}, {"id": 285262, "content": "成为朋友以后工作会很难推动", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252093}, {"id": 285263, "content": "你升职了她没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1096161}, {"id": 285264, "content": "突然跟你走亲近，这算什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1224508}, {"id": 285265, "content": "碰到 get 不到一个点的同事", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1254624}, {"id": 285266, "content": "1、大家面前好的跟亲姐妹一样，转头却互相说对方的不是。2、明知是品行不好的人，却依然能跟这种人打的火热。费解！", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1234388}, {"id": 285267, "content": "离职后再也没见过面", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191927}, {"id": 285268, "content": "午后工作突然想点杯咖啡，纠结我应不应该给同事们点一杯？", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255265}, {"id": 286292, "content": "懒得恭维、懒得陪笑、懒得附和，\n可惜还都照做了。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368942}, {"id": 285269, "content": "公司明明是挣钱的地方。", "image": null, "praise_count": 66, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1210344}, {"id": 285270, "content": "拜托咱俩真的不熟", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1352572}, {"id": 285271, "content": "同一个部门还要尔虞我诈", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1325810}, {"id": 285272, "content": "一个单位的时候有说有笑，换单位后比陌生人还陌生。", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1362410}, {"id": 285273, "content": "同事间的关系并没有自己所看到的那么好.", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1363492}, {"id": 285274, "content": "倾诉少一些，倾听多一些。呆得久不表示就能理解", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1263790}, {"id": 285786, "content": "作为一名财务，非要想方设法的问一些老板不想让员工知道的秘密，我也很无奈呀。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366686}, {"id": 285275, "content": "因为前同事认识了一些共同好友，可是这些人并不知道前同事人品有多差。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 908126}, {"id": 285276, "content": "愚善的人觉得自己和身边谁谁关系都好，该说给她戳破这个美梦还是让她继续圣母等撞板??", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1305122}, {"id": 285277, "content": "职场无朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1363529}, {"id": 285278, "content": "往往你对人家掏心掏肺了，人家却只觉得你是个职场傻瓜", "image": null, "praise_count": 67, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1363528}, {"id": 285280, "content": "潜规则…还有不明所以的针锋相对", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1363546}, {"id": 285281, "content": "没呆过办公室", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098071}, {"id": 285283, "content": "做最住在真转在真转我咿呀咿呀哟哦里咯几个很啦咯啦咯啦咯啦咯啦咯啦咯啦咯啦咯啦咯啦咯啦咯啦咯啦咯啦咯啦咯啦咯啦咯啦咯啦咯啦啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359962}, {"id": 285284, "content": "我就想看看有多少和我一样的大学生来看这个", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871583}, {"id": 285286, "content": "职场上找友情就像青楼里找爱情一样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 61, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1363619}, {"id": 285287, "content": "还没上职场的我来看看", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1188058}, {"id": 285288, "content": "我本是个安份与人无争的人，但偏偏被人视为其竞争上位的对手", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1339372}, {"id": 285289, "content": "圈子很小，好好做人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1363655}, {"id": 285290, "content": "被同部门的同事，“热情”的追问工资多少。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680554}, {"id": 295018, "content": "没有遇到过，本来就和同事不熟，配合工作而已", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1407567}, {"id": 285291, "content": "当面一套背后一套真的够了啊。真不用跟我表现得特别好然后背后捅刀子", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 295072}, {"id": 285292, "content": "不要和同事卖惨，他们只是看笑话", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1229673}, {"id": 285293, "content": "莫名的不知道把谁给惹了  怪我咯。。", "image": "img/option/option/20180604163605kAeZdMHlyIS7hpRL", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1363667}, {"id": 285295, "content": "在一个办公室，甚至无话不谈到夫妻生活，一旦离开连电话都没有一通", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 404676}, {"id": 285296, "content": "加入一家公司，很想为公司做点什么，主管领导却不信任自己，并坚信他自己才是忠心耿耿的一个。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1363686}]}